data.description: Absolutey Gorgeous 1 story home in sought after neighborhood of the Commons of Lake Houston. This beauty sits on a quiet cul-de-sac lot that is over an acre of land. Soaring 10' ceilings with amazing crown molding throughout. The recent upgrades are endless! Brand new floors, Kitchen Cabinets and Huge Walk-in pantry. You will love the Awesome open concept, with beautiful tile floors and freshly painted throughout the home. Newly updated stack stone fireplace and rustic wood accent wall give the living area a cozy feel! Wonderful office space, library, or can be used as a 4th bedroom! The Primary Bathroom has double sinks, separate claw tub, and huge shower! A fully screened in porch is another amazing feature of this home! Drink your morning coffee and listen to the quiet wilderness all year long! Schedule a showing today & make this beautiful home and property yours.
